<ITEM><LABEL><HI>Ver&s;.</HI> 7.</LABEL> The &s;ame came for a witne&s;s, to bear witne&s;s of the light, that all men through him might believe.</ITEM>
<ITEM><LABEL><HI>Ver&s;.</HI> 8.</LABEL> He was not that light, but was &s;ent to bear witne<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> of that light.</ITEM>
<ITEM><PB N="ix" REF="013006_0008_0F8FAAED679D8A60">
<LABEL><HI>Ver&s;.</HI> 9.</LABEL> That was the true light, which lighteth every man that cometh into the world.</ITEM>
